values.HIBER: The default Hiber set of features including Mission Control and the API
values.HILO: A limited set of features corresponding to the HiberHilo product.
values.MODEM_CREATION: Required to manually create modems using the ModemService.
values.EARLY_ACCESS: Used for organizations that get early access to features.
values.EXPERIMENTAL: Used for organizations that get access to experimental features. e.g. feature work in progress.
values.BI_TOOLING_BETA: Integrate BI tooling in the Mission Control interface.
